legacy.full_text:
Why don’t LLMs like #ChatGPT remember what you say?
@bobvanluijt  (CEO of @weaviate_io) explains how vector databases make #LLMs stateful, and powerful.

🎥 Watch his full talk with @blwiertz  at the latest “#AI Fireside Chat” &amp; get future events invites with the link in our bio! https://t.co/17GtFxN9dH

We're not surfing on AI. Proof is, you could've met these two folks in 2019 at the very same conference.
But how cool is it that, six years later, they’re back to blow our minds again with their cutting-edge AI workflows?
--
@Dimillian  https://t.co/fgk2LS3vbm
